CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 20, 1959, pg. A1, reads: "Reception For Foster Parents - Foster parents were entertained last week at a reception given for them by the Family and Children's Service. Two pairs of devoted foster parents, above, were pointed out as typical examples of the wonderful people who take children to their hearts.  Left: Mr. and Mrs. David M. Carey.  Right: Mr. and Mrs. Paul Silvers. - Harris Photo.
TitMainTitle: David M. Carey, Mrs. Carey and Mrs. Silvers holding teacups, and Paul Silvers standing in interior for reception for foster parents by Family and Children's Service
